    "disclaimer": "This calculator decodes standard IEC 60062 resistor color codes for 4-band and 5-band resistors. Some specialty resistors use different coding schemes.",
    "formulaLatex": "R_{4\\text{-band}} = (d_1 \\times 10 + d_2) \\times M, \\quad R_{5\\text{-band}} = (d_1 \\times 100 + d_2 \\times 10 + d_3) \\times M",
